		"notes": [
			{
				"category": "summary",
				"text": "An update for screen is now available for Red Hat Enterprise Linux 7.7 Advanced Update Support, Red Hat Enterprise Linux 7.7 Telco Extended Update Support, and Red Hat Enterprise Linux 7.7 Update Services for SAP Solutions.\n\nRed Hat Product Security has rated this update as having a security impact of Important. A Common Vulnerability Scoring System (CVSS) base score, which gives a detailed severity rating, is available for each vulnerability from the CVE link(s) in the References section.",
				"title": "Topic"
			},
			{
				"category": "general",
				"text": "The screen utility allows users to have multiple logins on a single terminal.\n\nSecurity Fix(es):\n\n* screen: crash when processing combining chars (CVE-2021-26937)\n\nFor more details about the security issue(s), including the impact, a CVSS score, acknowledgments, and other related information, refer to the CVE page(s) listed in the References section.",
				"title": "Details"
			},
